 * 2. Retrieve the newly created bookmark by its ID using GET /favoritesPersonalization/bookmarks/{id} and
 *    validate the returned fields.
 * 3. Attempt to retrieve a bookmark with a random non-existent UUID and verify a 404 (not found) or error occurs.
